flowchart TD
    U[Users/API Clients] --> LB[Load Balancer]
    LB --> API[API stateless replicas]
    API --> PG[(PostgreSQL Cluster)]
    API --> Redis[(Redis Cache / Rate Limit)]
    API --> MQ[Message Queue]
    MQ --> DW[Discovery Workers]
    MQ --> IW[Import Workers]
    MQ --> GW[Graph Workers]
    MQ --> RW[Reporting Workers]
    DW --> PG
    IW --> PG
    GW --> PG
    RW --> S3[(Object Storage)]
